cky37.github.io/epicseven-tools/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstocky37.github.io%2Fepicseven-tools%2F&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=eece3d1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://stocky37.github.io/epicseven-tools/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">露營好感計算機</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://budandan.github.io/e7-lab-team-optimizer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbudandan.github.io%2Fe7-lab-team-optimizer%2F&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=d3963bea\" target=\"_blank\">https://budandan.github.io/e7-lab-team-optimizer/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Raid 攻略</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1hFz8lTVCNdv8wUE1qbUYKd42iQMCesLpeFgNxmJ3zfc/preview#slide=id.g4e4c6ec9ea_0_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fpresentation%2Fd%2F1hFz8lTVCNdv8wUE1qbUYKd42iQMCesLpeFgNxmJ3zfc%2Fpreview%23slide%3Did.g4e4c6ec9ea_0_8&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=8be2a556\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1hFz8lTVCNdv8wUE1qbUYKd42iQMCesLpeFgNxmJ3zfc/preview#slide=id.g4e4c6ec9ea_0_8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>催化劑位置圖</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guuuqtd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fguuuqtd.png&h=b5118cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">公會</span></strong></span><br />\n要入會請留game 名<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>國際服</strong></span><br />\n<strong>LIHKG</strong><br />\n<strong>LIHKGUILD</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>亞服</strong></span><br />\n<strong>疾風亂舞</strong><br />\n<strong>LIHKG</strong><br />\n<strong>零課清泉</strong><br />\n<strong>rebirth</strong><br />\n<strong>連登聯盟</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新手入門</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Hr-kigyoUOD-FAr_TqSFjnxWJGv7JOhQJ5u44ENGNyo/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1Hr-kigyoUOD-FAr_TqSFjnxWJGv7JOhQJ5u44ENGNyo%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=434011c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Hr-kigyoUOD-FAr_TqSFjnxWJGv7JOhQJ5u44ENGNyo/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新手抽卡推薦</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n補師優先<br />\n水奶(Angelica/ 安潔莉卡) &gt;火奶(Achates/ 雅卡泰絲) / 木奶(Destina/ 戴絲蒂娜)<br />\n<br />\n輸出其次<br />\n木刺(Vildred/ 維瑞德/ 木25)，木飛劍(Iseria/ 伊賽麗亞)，親生仔(Cidd/ 席德)，火法(Aramintha/ 雅拉敏塔 /火團長)，火槍(Schuri/ 修里)，火拳(Ken/ 肯恩)，火斧(Ravi/ 蘿菲)，水卡琳(Karin)，水刺(Sez/ 賽茲)，<br />\n<br />\n神器待補<br />\n四星：塵埃惡魔 (Dust Devil)，羅沙哈勒戈納 (Rosa Hargana)，無限提籃 (Infinity Basket)，靈藥的試管 (Wondrous Potion Vial) 等等<br />\n五星：大部分都要得過<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新手買帳角色推薦</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<strong>聖女(Diene/ 迪埃妮)</strong>：限定角，超強輔助角，絕大部分content都用得到<br />\n<strong>龍女(Luna/ 露娜)</strong>：限定角，超強輸出，龍11主力。但作為輸出角可以用其他角色代替，例如免費三星轉職暗槍<br />\n<strong>明星(Tamarinne/ 塔瑪林爾)</strong>：強力奶，夾攻﹑拉條﹑群補﹑消debuff + 清對面buff﹑加攻集於一身，冇聖女可以要明星，又係夠過絕大部分content。另外最好有埋<strong>木飛劍</strong>，減變身CD一開場就可以開大變身瘋狂補/輸出<br />\n<strong>木扇(Bellona/ 維爾蘿娜)</strong>：單體打boss計percentage削血，群體破防兼大力，又係乜content都啱用<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">術語及機制</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<ins><strong>日常</strong></ins><br />\n狗糧/肥料(Fodder)：升角色星用嘅怪物/狼，詳情參考Google Doc《新手入門》文章<br />\n<br />\n121：限定角色保底活動，第121抽必中<br />\n<br />\n光暗抽：通關普通10-10關後開放月光召喚(Moonlight Summon, ML)，可用金光傳承石於商店交換銀河書籤即可到召喚頁面抽角。銀河書籤亦可由迷宮逆襲中取得。歡迎各位貼圖分享抽光暗角的樂與悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n深淵：打到就打，每日打唔到都可以淨化3次嚟拎雌蕊聖葉，深淵嘅吸血裝同迷宮裝係新手啱用嘅好裝備<br />\n<br />\n迷宮：唔使全部行晒，優先行去拎晒d迷宮裝備先，之後就落下一層。每日記得入去第一個迷宮左上搵商人買下好野，買完放棄關卡出嚟唔會扣入場券<br />\n<br />\nRaid：迷宮逆襲，靚裝同催化劑來源之一<br />\n<br />\n討伐：四屬boss&mdash;火龍﹑石像﹑女妖﹑暗蟲。多數聚焦打火龍，因為會跌裝備同埋材料用嚟做速度﹑暴擊同命中set，輸出同輔助角色要用到速度裝 <br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>戰鬥</strong></ins><br />\n拉條：增加己方速攻值(Combat Readiness)，戰鬥畫面左面行動條睇到邊個係一下個行動。速度快就行快d，多d turns。拉條可以令自己隊友可以更快行動。<br />\n<br />\n命中：<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>裝備</strong></ins><br />\nT1-T6：<br />\nRoll：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新手必打: 迷宮金寶箱位置圖</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=34880&amp;snA=555&amp;tnum=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D34880%26snA%3D555%26tnum%3D1&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=236f8a96\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=34880&amp;snA=555&amp;tnum=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"54677570fc9348befc157f230ee19aee72fd76af","tid":1154460,"uid":43576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:14:00.000Z","msg":"其實我有冇開錯post? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見94沉咗落底, 好似未有人開95<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173b22e0328703a8ae8762cd2091d0eaf0638a88","tid":1154460,"uid":43576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:15:39.000Z","msg":"從來未試過開post, 如有搞錯請各位巴打見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=